nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars The Complete Season One

Star Wars: The Clone Wars The Complete Season One is a three-disc Blu-ray or four-disc DVD box set of the 2008–2009 first season of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series. It was first released by Warner Home Video on November 3, 2009.
